  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Liberté, Égalité, Fraternité, Méca. 😎</strong><br>Fire up the mechs, it’s time to start a revolution! <strong>Bonaparte: A Mechanized Revolution</strong> is available now in a glorious full edition that will let you play through your vision for the alternate, Colossi-shaped future of France!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/537e4c284c2c6bdc8be83ad57276779a.avif?t=1762781982\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>Defend, oppose, or reform the monarchy with these added features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unit veterancy (to provide more significant units and reward successful tactical gameplay)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New languages (Chinese - Simplified, Chinese - Traditional, Japanese, Korean, Spanish, and German)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New mechs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements (gotta catch ‘em all!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updated music to set the mood for your Revolution.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We can’t wait to see how your revolution unfolds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking to meet fellow revolutionaries? We also have a Discord, come join us! Strategize, suggest new ideas, or use our dedicated bug channel for reporting and one-on-one support!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1789, Paris. Take Napoleon’s place in an alternate history as Céline or César Bonaparte in this ideology driven, turn-based strategy journey. Defend, reform or oppose the monarchy and write your own alternative history by combining cunning political skills and tactical military prowess.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/490702d4cbbc32e5e93dc275d569e47c.poster.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/490702d4cbbc32e5e93dc275d569e47c.webm?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/490702d4cbbc32e5e93dc275d569e47c.mp4?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f3bb9d07be9b80200fb415656b5c2672.webp?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LEAD OR OPPOSE THE REVOLUTION THAT CHANGED THE WESTERN WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as an alternate Bonaparte and rewrite History by fighting for your ideals. Choose to defend the King, reform the monarchy, or embrace the revolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/9a0ecd0d4ea4218efbc7dd0cf582c5e9.poster.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/9a0ecd0d4ea4218efbc7dd0cf582c5e9.webm?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/9a0ecd0d4ea4218efbc7dd0cf582c5e9.mp4?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/2d1309ce8206818e6eca5512e31c8ea2.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f3bb9d07be9b80200fb415656b5c2672.webp?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER MECHANIZED TACTICAL BATTLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Recruit soldiers, construct mighty Colossi, improve your armies and face your opponents on the battlefield in tense turn-based combat. Outmaneuver the enemy on the battlefield, and exploit their weaknesses to prevail against all odds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/e5caf81aa209253ccc55e2482b7d02d2.poster.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/e5caf81aa209253ccc55e2482b7d02d2.webm?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/e5caf81aa209253ccc55e2482b7d02d2.mp4?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/637f693ae8223123693e25cf3cbda924.poster.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/637f693ae8223123693e25cf3cbda924.webm?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/637f693ae8223123693e25cf3cbda924.mp4?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f3bb9d07be9b80200fb415656b5c2672.webp?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MANIPULATE AN INTRICATE POLITICAL SYSTEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join, fight or overthrow famous historical characters and factions brought to life in a political simulation. Military might alone cannot insure victory, and your ability to navigate the complex political landscape will be an essential tool to reshape France to match your ideals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f5c36849c33f46ccd33d092fe95bdad4.poster.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f5c36849c33f46ccd33d092fe95bdad4.webm?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f5c36849c33f46ccd33d092fe95bdad4.mp4?t=1762781982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/e0ab5a2c9714548a900ce6310e9a28a6.avif?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560340/extras/f3bb9d07be9b80200fb415656b5c2672.webp?t=1762781982\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JOIN THE COMMUNITY & GUIDE THE REVOLUTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist the game and join our Discord community where you will be able to join special opportunities, share feedback, swap strategies or brag about your victories. Help guide the French Revolutionary strategy from within!</p>",
